      @GetMapping("/computer/search") public List<Computer> SearchComputer​(@RequestParam(defaultValue="") String brand, @RequestParam(defaultValue="") String model, @RequestParam(defaultValue="") String screenSize, @RequestParam(defaultValue="0") float minprice, @RequestParam(defaultValue="9999999") float maxprice, @RequestParam(defaultValue="0") int minstoragecapacity, @RequestParam(defaultValue="9999999") int maxstoragecapacity, @RequestParam(defaultValue="") String processor, @RequestParam(defaultValue="") String screenResolution, @RequestParam(defaultValue="0") int minmemory, @RequestParam(defaultValue="9999999") int maxmemory)
      Search through computers with optional parameters
      Parameters:
      brand - Optional URL parameter for computer brand
      model - Optional URL parameter for computer model
      screenSize - Optional URL parameter for computer screen size
      minprice - Optional URL parameter for minimum price. Default is 0
      maxprice - Optional URL parameter for maximum price. Default is 9999999
      minstoragecapacity - Optional URL parameter for minimum storage capacity. Default is 0
      maxstoragecapacity - Optional URL parameter for maximum storage capacity. Default is 9999999
      processor - Optional URL parameter for processor model
      screenResolution - Optional URL parameter for screenResolution
      minmemory - optional URL parameter for minimum device memory. Default is 0
      maxmemory - optional URL parameter for maximum device memory. Default is 9999999
      Returns:
      JSONArray of requested computers
